descript.abstract: Buffer of Channel Islands National Park fox trapping grids for Santa Rosa Island. Input dataset is H:\Data\nrdata\monitoring\FoxTrapGrids.shp buffered to 900 meters and clipped to CUSP shoreline (https://shoreline.noaa.gov/data/datasheets/cusp.html). Data was projected to Nad83 UTM Zone 10 to match R analysis for annual fox density estimates. Rocky Rudolph 3/4/2019
